These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  bartender, teacher, dancer, journalist, lawyer, pilot, engineer
There are 7 different nationalities: indonesian, italian, egyptian, colombian, indian, dutch, spanish
 1. the journalist is on the left of the colombian##1
 2. the indian is the journalist##1
 3. the engineer is on the right of the pilot##1
 4. the egyptian is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the dancer is in the middle##1
 6. the indonesian is on the far left##1
 7. the lawyer is the indonesian##1
 8. the bartender is on the right of the dutch##1
 9. the egyptian is on the left of the italian##1
10. the colombian is on the left of the dancer##1
11. the engineer is on the right of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | lawyer | journalist | teacher | dancer | bartender | pilot | engineer |
| Nationality   | indonesian    | indian   | colombian      | dutch | egyptian    | italian    | spanish         |

