.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
There 7 different types of food: cherry, kale, mango, lemon, asparagus, radish, peas
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: classical, reggae, metal, jazz, hip-hop, r&b, salsa
 1. the fan of hip-hop is the person eating lemon##1
 2. the person eating radish is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 3. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
 4. the person eating kale is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
 5. the person eating lemon is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 6. the person eating radish is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 7. the fan of hip-hop is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 9. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person eating mango##1
10. the person eating lemon is on the left of the fan of classical##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Food          | cherry | kale | asparagus | lemon | radish | peas | mango |
| Music-Genre   | reggae      | metal   | jazz   | hip-hop      | classical       | salsa       | r&b     |

