.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-3::.
There 7 different types of food: banana, pomegranate, avocado, radish, strawberry, cranberry, pumpkin
The people have 7 different jobs:  project-manager, analyst, musician, designer, paramedic, chef, doctor
 1. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
 2. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the doctor##1
 3. the analyst is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
 4. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
 5. the project-manager is the person eating strawberry##1
 6. the musician is on the right of the analyst##1
 7. the analyst is on the left of the musician##1
 8. the analyst is on the right of the designer##1
 9. the person eating cranberry is the designer##1
10. the person eating avocado is on the right of the project-manager##1
11. the designer is in the middle##1
12. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the paramedic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |   3    |      4       |     5      |    6     |     7     |
| Food   | pomegranate | strawberry     | avocado  | cranberry       | banana       | pumpkin  | radish   |
| Job    | chef  | project-manager | doctor | designer | analyst | musician | paramedic |

