.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: d&b, hip-hop, soul, electronic, techno, pop, ambient
There are 7 different nationalities: japanese, spanish, french, brazilian, american, chinese, british
 1. the fan of techno is the spanish##1
 2. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 3. the chinese is on the right of the french##1
 4. the japanese is on the right of the fan of techno##1
 5. the fan of techno is on the left of the fan of d&b##1
 6. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
 7. the french is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the right of the chinese##1
 9. the fan of soul is the american##1
10. the american is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
11. the british is the fan of hip-hop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | ambient     | electronic     | soul      | hip-hop | techno      | d&b     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | french | chinese | american | british | spanish | japanese |

