.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: skydiving, photography, collecting, filmmaking, camping, reading, puzzles
7 different pets are kept: bird, lizard, rat, rabbit, ferret, chinchilla, cat
 1. the person who's hobby is photography is the owner of the cat##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
10. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | photography | collecting | reading     | filmmaking | puzzles | camping | skydiving |
| Pet     | cat   | rat    | ferret | chinchilla     | bird         | rabbit     | lizard        |

