.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-6::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, mirinda, tea, fanta, water, lemonade
The people use 7 different means of transport: car, boat, helicopter, scooter, subway, airplane, motorbike
 1. the person drinking water is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 2. the person drinking cola is the person driving the car##1
 3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
 5. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person drinking tea is in the middle##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 9. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4     |    5    |   6   |      7      |
| Beverage    | mirinda | water   | cola | tea | lemonade  | fanta | milk |
| Transport   | scooter   | subway | car | airplane     | boat | motorbike | helicopter   |

