.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: romance, sports, comedy, spy, musical, western, scientific
The people use 7 different means of transport: subway, scooter, taxi, train, airplane, bus, quad-bike
 1. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 2. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
 3. the person watching scientific movies is the person driving the train##1
 4. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
 5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the person driving the subway is the person watching comedy movies##1
 8. the person watching musical movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
10. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance  | scientific | spy | musical | western     | sports | comedy |
| Transport     | bus | train      | quad-bike | taxi    | airplane | scooter   | subway  |

