 4. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
 6. the person who's hobby is reading is the person driving the airplane##1
 7. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 9. the person who's hobby is drawing is in the middle##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |       4       |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Hobby       | board-games   | singing | chess | drawing | traveling     | reading | photography |
| Transport   | bike | motorbike      | jet-ski        | ship         | bus | airplane     | van |

