 6. the person driving the motorbike is the person eating apricot##1
 7. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating onion##1
 8. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 9. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1
10. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
11. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person eating apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |   3    |    4     |   5    |     6      |   7    |
