.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-13::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: card-games, camping, dancing, board-games, skydiving, hiking, woodworking
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: drama, fantasy, time-travel, spy, scientific, thriller, adventure
 1. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 3. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 6. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 8. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's hobby is camping##1
 9. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
10. the person who's hobby is card-games is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |     6     |    7     |
| Hobby         | hiking | camping   | woodworking | card-games | skydiving | board-games | dancing  |
| Movie-Genre   | spy  | scientific | adventure  | time-travel | thriller | drama     | fantasy |

