 4. the person driving the car is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
 5. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 6. the person driving the airplane is the person watching crime movies##1
 7. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 9. the person watching action movies is in the middle##1
10. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
